 class="sector">Burgess Hill</span><span class="sector">Haywards Heath</span><span class="sector">Hassocks</span></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 24px;"><div class="kicker">Why AMPM</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Local, accountable,<br>one team.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span>On your doorstep</span></h4><ul><li><strong>Local base</strong> — run from Burgess Hill, around 15 miles north, so a named contact is on site quickly and back to you within the day.</li><li><strong>Coastal envelope experience</strong> — seafront and exposed buildings take a beating from salt, wind and driving rain; we weatherproof, reclad and detail the fabric to hold up to it.</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span>One accountable team</span></h4><ul><li><strong>Built for hospitality &amp; education</strong> — phased, out-of-hours works around hotels, venues and campuses, so trading and term-time keep running while we work.</li><li><strong>One team for the lot</strong> — MEPH, fit-out, fabric and external works self-delivered under one programme, so the services, the space and the building hand over together.</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">FAQs</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Brighton &amp; Hove questions,<br>answered.</h2></div><div class="faq reveal in"><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you cover Brighton and Hove?</summary><p>Yes — across the whole of Brighton &amp; Hove. We're based in Burgess Hill, West Sussex, around 15 miles north of the city, so we're genuinely local and a named contact is on site quickly.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you work on seafront / coastal buildings?</summary><p>Yes. Coastal and seafront buildings take constant salt exposure, wind and driving rain, so the envelope has to be right. We handle weatherproofing, façade repair, recladding, glazing and roofing detailed for that exposure, to Part L and the relevant fabric standards.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you work with hotels and venues in Brighton?</summary><p>Yes. Most hospitality work is phased around a trading building — out-of-hours isolations, temporary services and room-by-room or area-by-area handover — so the hotel or venue keeps operating while we work.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which areas do you cover?</summary><p>London and the South East, including Sussex, Surrey, Kent, Hampshire and Berkshire.</p></details></div></section><section class="sec tight line-top"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 24px;"><div class="kicker">Our service lines</div><h2 class="dhead sm">One contractor,<br>four service lines.</h2></div><div class="otherlines reveal in"><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Commercial</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Fabric</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Groundworks</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div></div></section></div><section class="band" data-nav-dark="true" style="background: var(--m-green); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div class="shell"><div class="cta-split reveal in"><div><div class="kicker on-dark">Talk to us about MEPH</div><h2 class="dhead sm" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Scope, programme,<br>stage — send it over.</h2><p class="body" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); margin-top: 16px;">A named contact, not a sales team, comes back within 24 hours. Include the package,